data.description: Be ready to Dive In this Spring! Sparkling pool with great outdoor entertainment area! Rare find in Deer Valley Community - 2Bedroom/2Bath with office area, large vaulted greatroom, open dining area with bar overlooking greatroom. You will love the covered screen porch and covered outdoor entertainment area. This home sits on a large cul-de-sac .44 acre lot. Pool area is fenced with large green space on each side of home. This one owner home has been very well maintained. Pool serviced by professional pool company with new liner installed 3 years ago. Conveniently located off of Murphy Mill Road and zoned for Highlands Elementary. Call today to see this great home!
